      • getPreProcessors

        public java.util.List<IPreProcessingStrategy> getPreProcessors()
        Description copied from interface: IDetector
        Specify the preprocessors required for this detector.

        The individual strategies in the list can be produced using the generic methods IPreProcessingStrategy.of(String, Class...) or IPreProcessingStrategy.of(String, boolean, Class...) in the interface, or using a fully custom IPreProcessingStrategy class.

        The string name of each of the strategies is used as the key reference in the preprocessed dataset given to the IDetector.buildWorkers(List) method

        Returns:
        a list of the required preprocessing strategies
